{"tid":1478351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急 廣傳]有一堆黑黑實實後生仔落左黎做spy","createTime":"2019-08-16T13:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T01:41:56.000Z","uid":137048,"like":93,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"4b3689960410774d6516f82dd01c21f669dd0519","tid":1478351,"uid":137048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"借朋友acc 出<br />\n<br />\n以下係一個做入境既朋友講的：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日下午4點幾，落馬洲支線有好多後生仔落黎，好明顯係一團人，因為見到咁多人，同事去問佢地落黎做乜<br />\n佢地答踩單車 但去邊踩答唔出<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野已經好奇怪，之後入境朋友就叫佢地開背囊<br />\n<br />\n睇左背囊,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全部都拎左單車頭盔，同幾件黑色T</span></span><br />\n佢地全部都交代唔到究竟要去邊<br />\n<br />\n入境前線已經盡做<br />\n佢地人數太多截唔哂<br />\n大部分後生仔同埋第一次來港<br />\n唔止福建，乜野省份都有<br />\n<br />\n星期日各位小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無圖，身份關係影唔到相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他關口我相信都有一樣情況出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位巴絲問下四圍索下料<br />\n因為做入境既朋友應該都發覺<br />\n<br />\n大家呢排小心<br />\n唔係想有白色恐怖定乜<br />\n但敵在暗 我地在明<br />\n小心駛得萬年船<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家加油！818 齊上齊落 唔好落單</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要保護身邊每一位戰友<br />\n一個都不能少！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b850903d92886c1433566ed9b450f46b74d36fd9","tid":1478351,"uid":303567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"OMG!!! Again!!!!"},{"pid":"a4ab513b2b468a1ab84bf1f7b0f9105468cb0f39","tid":1478351,"uid":303567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:11:06.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!!! 又係咁！大家要小心"},{"pid":